Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  有點心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:29.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,-----OP-----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想製作父親節的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:15.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,乳之日？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:15.78,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：日語中的「父の日」和「乳の日」諧音。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,護符
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然有點難  就做這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我也一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:23.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我希望自己一個人完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,父親節的禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太很溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真期待翔太的禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:45.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,護符啊  很多人類都帶著的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:49.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,護符真的有效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是心理安慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我總是一起燒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還真是過於真實的經驗之談
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:03:00.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,賦予魔術的護符可是有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是不明白為什麼乳之日要送護符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞  你從剛才開始就在說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看嘛  畢竟是乳之日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了  大奶大奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:33.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正品已經賣光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個評價很差沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,首先是獨角獸的角和飛龍的血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:04.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,搗碎的人面樹的樹枝加上乾燥的藍玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,全部放進去之後煮一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等到刺激性氣味消散之後施加融合魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我還是來幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這次的活動任務還真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:35.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實我在製作護符作為父親節的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是並不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明是按照魔法書上寫的步驟做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼做不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想向父親展現我的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣下去根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我需要快點獨當一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就和遊戲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想打倒比自己等級更高的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,自然是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是如果你一定要打的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就思考一下製作者的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,製作者的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  遊戲是設定好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以他們只會按照製作者的想法運作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:23.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以  只要思考製作者是基於什麼想法製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他們想讓玩家怎麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能讀懂這種心理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就能自然而然地找到通關之路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,瀧也一直在往這種方向奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:41.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,製作方可是在很辛苦地思考該怎麼騙過玩家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,製作者的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我再努力看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:56.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有什麼需要的條件是沒有記載在魔法書裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:03.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快看  露科亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,護符完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,做得好  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我試著思考了一下作者的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,調查了他寫魔法書的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:23.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,發現是在海拔為負數  類似這邊死海一樣地方寫成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我試著升高了房間的氣壓模擬同樣的環境…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行  我才不會告訴你這個汙穢的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,被表揚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我還要繼續努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  有好好努力過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天是乳之日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快住手
Comment: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:23.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/敲肩膀券
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:20.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,敲肩膀券？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼要送我禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天也不是我生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為是父親節
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是母親嗎
Comment: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第八話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.99,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}世界上唯一的（請自行填上喜歡的詞語）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我無法理解的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龍不會感冒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:56.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,區區病毒怎麼能在我的體內存活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,該去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這種程度怎麼能請假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是不是很嚴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是去不成公司了  得打個電話過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:25.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跟她說我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:30.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個  瀧谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:37.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然小林喝了藥之後已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有沒有我能做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:45.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼對待感冒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能變小之後去消滅引起感冒的病菌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:53.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然做得到  但是可能連小林的身體一起破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:54.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看護？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是說需要的是女僕之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林現在正需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,必須拚盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:14.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是看護是要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給她吃些好吃的就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,木炭或者石炭之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:24.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林不是火焰龍也不是爐灶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我只知道怎麼讓人生病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不會治病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也學學守護啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,餵她吃些易消化的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:39.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給腦袋降溫  或者給她擦擦汗就行了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,必須要問三個人才能得到像樣點的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我的交友圈還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總之先找些易消化的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有什麼適合的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,畢竟我大部分的東西都能消化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雜燴粥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像是很簡單的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:01.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,酸奶…我記得康娜的好像還放在冰箱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,烏冬  果凍  香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再加上些甜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,完成了  這是雜燴粥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她都難得做了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,直接說這東西不能吃  有點不識趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:20.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看來要讓她理解食物搭配太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃得真香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次記得正常地按食譜做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正常地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你出了很多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓我幫你擦擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:52.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事  心跳好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:01.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林平時能讓大家覺得是個很可靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還是第一次見到她如此虛弱的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我見過被瘟疫摧毀的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也見過因瘟疫而走向滅亡的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒有人會讓重要之物遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但沒有什麼東西是無法破壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,尤其對於我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我什麼都能破壞才會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:34.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  你幫我看好小林
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然有不死之秘藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但小林不喜歡這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼至少得找來些能治病的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然可能會很艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我還是要去找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:03.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我所珍視的小林還在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好地睡一覺之後  這病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林你好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再吃一次藥和再睡一覺就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:30.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  氣喘吁吁的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  我跑遍了許多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我找到了特效藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:47.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不會又是摻了些什麼奇怪的東西進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:57.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊  這個藥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.42,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,我是真的很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:18.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,實際上我並不知道是不是真的起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但只要是看到她這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,無論吃的是什麼我都會說「起效了」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個…可能是副作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為是給獸人用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這副樣子怎麼上班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Comment: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/朧家小賣部
Comment: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/零食
Comment: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有個娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是誰忘在這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還做得挺精緻的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是高檔品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,應該要送回失主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等到明天自然就會回來認領的吧
Comment: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/小賣部
Comment: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/零食
Comment: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/遊戲
Comment: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.57,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\pos(1302.4,456.6)\c&H282828&}-第二天-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.57,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs60\pos(1032,956.857)\frz2.707\b1}失\N物\N招\N領
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像沒回來認領呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們去找失主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,首先要在周圍打聽情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,阿竹你也來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我對你不是很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小賣部的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們知道這個娃娃是誰的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:46.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,竹人和伊露露姐姐是在一起交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你胡說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不是在陪我一起找失主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也問問那邊的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,根本沒在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒有人知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,哪有這麼簡單就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:11.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,話說回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,會不會不是忘掉而是特意遺棄的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不交給警察局算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒有其他能幫忙的人了嗎
Comment: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/小賣部
Comment: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/零食
Comment: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我帶幫手來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:46.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,事情我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我好像沒什麼能幫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  小林的話肯定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這就是伊露露口中的小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,乍一看很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但後面那個金髮女僕是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經習慣了嗎  居然如此淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,平日裡就讓她做這類事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙肯定不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拍張照在網上找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露你不是可以用魔法加強嗅覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼突然間就讓她扮狗玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經調教好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,竹人  你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能接受小林調教的只有我托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別再添油加醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  我知道是什麼味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:36.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個  送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是什麼  我可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是為了小伊露露做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:51.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我會好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,走到隔壁鎮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓繼續你陪著我也不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你可以先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:17.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還有很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的是被遺棄的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,撿到的時候還帶有一絲溫熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定到前一秒都還抱在懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  會淋濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,味道也要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不是回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,天陰下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,像要下雨一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:20.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,阿竹  我曾經丟棄過一個我所珍視的娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而直到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都在後悔為什麼沒有撿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個娃娃肯定也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:43.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那看來得認真找到主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:44.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:48.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:49.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:54.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她剛從哪出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,通過個人訂製的店鋪知道失主是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,詢問過店家以後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為失主經常會去做保養
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以店裡的人也都記得是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:09.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道失主是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她希望你能把娃娃帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,地址也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以你是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給各位添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:28.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是抱著遺棄的心情把娃娃放在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想著你們可能會將其裝飾在店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我已經是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,卻被朋友嘲笑小孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是遺棄了之後一直在懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,事到如今還在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果還能撿回來的話就撿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:50.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跟她說聲「歡迎回家」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:07.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了  伊露露  去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能陪著伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也沒做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:15.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你也濕了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一起洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別光著身子來我這
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,又不是在外面  在浴室裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好害羞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你這是什麼歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是青春洋溢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是阿竹娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:40.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笨…你把娃娃夾在什麼地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,放這裡最安心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,安心？
Comment: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/朧家小賣部
Comment: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/零食
Comment: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:46.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不阿竹也夾進來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不知羞恥嗎
